OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry evening, but outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fwill gradually spread eastwards
OL,8,Fovernight. The rain turning heavier
OL,9,Fand more persistent by dawn. A breezy
OL,10,Fbut mild night to come.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA wet morning with the rain
OL,13,Fheavy in places. The rain gradually
OL,14,Feasing from the west throughout the
OL,15,Fafternoon with brighter but showery
OL,16,Fweather following. Feeling cool for
OL,17,Fearly June.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
